    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 platform, featuring a 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. Maintained to an exacting standard, this vehicle features documented rod bearing replacement and a pristine subframe. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission delivers seamless torque vectoring through the variable M differential lock, while the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) ensures the suspension kinematics remain sharp and responsive. With its carbon-fiber roof lowering the center of gravity and a flawless factory finish, this chassis offers the mechanical purity and rigidity expected of a collector-grade performance machine.",
