      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its showroom-quality finish since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, entirely free from stone chips, swirl marks, or surface imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in an untouched state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no signs of creasing or wear, and the original factory scent lingers. Mechanically, this car is indistinguishable from new, backed by a comprehensive service history performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. Every component, from the precision-tuned engine to the high-fidelity sound system, functions with factory-spec accuracy. This is a rare, time-capsule opportunity for a buyer who demands a vehicle in its most pristine, absolute form.",
